I-I did no such thing.

164
00:05:45,457 --> 00:05:46,825
Dr. Webber!

165
00:05:46,910 --> 00:05:49,881
I promised Jo Wilson that if she
got me a spot in OB-GYN,

166
00:05:49,966 --> 00:05:51,764
I would see
the residency through,

167
00:05:51,849 --> 00:05:54,396
